OL,3,CFather of terror attack victim says
OL,4,Chis son's death must not be in vain
OL,6,FEarlier this year, an inquest into the
OL,7,F2020 stabbings concluded the deaths
OL,8,Fwere avoidable and found major
OL,9,Fproblems with intelligence sharing
OL,10,Fbetween authorities.
OL,12,FGary Furlong said: "At present,
OL,13,Fwithout massive investment, I have no
OL,14,Ffaith whatsoever and the Judge Coroner
OL,15,FSir Adrian Fulford also stated he is
OL,16,Fnot confident the changes will be
OL,17,Fthere to make a significant effect on
OL,18,Fthe future."
