OL,3,CFather of terror attack victim says
OL,4,Chis son's death must not be in vain
OL,6,FHe said: "It can't be one meeting, I
OL,7,Fthink that there has to be a review of
OL,8,Fthe process, it needs to be fed back
OL,9,Fto the families annually so I want
OL,10,Fthere to be an ongoing process...
OL,12,F"James always said to me and his mum,
OL,13,Fyou can't change the past, it's fixed
OL,14,Fbut you can learn from the past and
OL,15,Fchange the future."
